Source.Name: rocblas
Source.Summary: Next generation BLAS implementation for ROCm platform
Source.Description: rocBLAS is the AMD library for Basic Linear Algebra Subprograms (BLAS) on the ROCm platform. It is implemented in the HIP programming language and optimized for AMD GPUs.
